description: RawTools is a software that provides parsing and quantification of raw Thermo Orbitrap mass spectrometer data. RawTools software was used to process a set of injections (n = 140) from a prepared HeLa digest that were analyzed on an Orbitrap Velos to get summarized instrument performance metrics for quality control.
